        <h1>Shipping Policy</h1>

        <p>Confirmed orders will be shipped within 1-2 working days. Once shipped, they'll be delivered to you within 2-7 working days. Delivery times are influenced by product availability, geographic location of customers, customers shipping destination, and the courier partner's time-to-deliver in customer’s location.</p>

        <h2>Locations We Ship To</h2>
        <p>Kushmanda Cosmetics ships throughout India!</p>

        <h2>Shipping Charges</h2>
        <p>Shipping charge of INR 70 is applicable on all orders below INR 499/- (Payable), unless specified otherwise.</p>

        <h2>Order Tracking</h2>
        <p>You can log in to your whitewolf account and track your order in the 'My Orders' section. We will also send you an email with the tracking details once the order is shipped.</p>

        <h2>Non-Delivery Report</h2>
        <p>If your order shows delivered, but you haven’t received it, you need to report Non-Delivery of the order within 48 hours of receiving the delivery notification by emailing us at <a href="mailto:care@whitewolfindia.com">care@whitewolfindia.com</a> or contacting us via the chat support. After 48 hours, Kushmanda Cosmetics claims no liability.</p>

